apter`, XML catalog resolution, XSLT processor lookup, compiler adapter lookup, RMI adapters, and the direct `ClassConstants` constant-reading path. Preserving these tests keeps broad reachability coverage for `ant:ant:1.6` while removing only the single test that depends on unsupported isolated runtime classpath loading behavior.\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
